---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import "../styles/pages/services.css";
---

<Layout>
	<section class="service hero site-container col-2">
		<div class="service--inner">
			<h1>Cheap, Affordable Websites Made From Scratch That Make Conversions</h1>
			<p>I create websites that are modern and readable, ensuring your online presence not only looks great but also performs exceptionally.</p>

			<button class="btn cta--btn">Schedule Free Consulation</button>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="projects site-container">
		<div class="projects--inner">
			<h1>See The Work Itself</h1>

			<div class="projects--list col-4">
				<Card classes="project--item">
					<h3>Project 1</h3>
				</Card>
				<Card classes="project--item">
					<h3>Project 2</h3>
				</Card>
				<Card classes="project--item">
					<h3>Project 3</h3>
				</Card>
				<Card classes="project--item">
					<h3>Project 4</h3>
				</Card>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="problem site-container">
		<div class="problem">
			<h1>I Can Make Websites That Act As a Salesman </h1>
			<p>In today's digital landscape, your website isn't just an online brochureâ€”it's your most powerful sales tool, working 24/7 to connect with potential customers. Many businesses struggle with outdated, slow, or unengaging websites that deter visitors instead of drawing them in. This often results in missed opportunities, lost sales, and a significant disadvantage against competitors who have invested in a strong online presence. Without a modern, efficient, and user-friendly website, you're leaving money on the table and failing to capture the leads you deserve.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="benefits site-container col-2">
		<div class="benefits--text">
			<h1>This is Where I Come In</h2>
			<p>I create websites using custom solutions. No bloat, or long loading times, just pure performance and aesthetics tailored to your business needs.</p>
		</div>

		<ul class="benefits--card--container col-2">
			<Card classes="benefit--card">
				<h3 class="benefit--title">Security Handled</h3>
				<p class="benefit--description">Your website will be built with robust security measures to protect your data and your visitors.</p>
			</Card>

			<Card classes="benefit--card">
				<h3 class="benefit--title">Infinitely Scalable</h3>
				<p class="benefit--description">Designed to grow with your business, ensuring your website can handle increasing traffic and content without a hitch.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card classes="benefit--card">
				<h3 class="benefit--title">Fast Loading Times</h3>
				<p class="benefit--description">Optimized for speed, providing a seamless user experience that keeps visitors engaged and reduces bounce rates.</p>
			</Card>
			<Card classes="benefit--card">
				<h3 class="benefit--title">SEO Optimized</h3>
				<p class="benefit--description">Built with search engine best practices in mind, helping your site rank higher and attract more organic traffic.</p>
			</Card>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="how--to site-container">
		<h2>Here's how the process works</h2>

		<ul class="col-4">
			<li>**1. Discovery Call:** We start with a detailed conversation to understand your business, goals, and vision for your website.</li>
			<li>**2. Design Phase:** I'll create custom designs that align with your brand identity and user experience best practices.</li>
			<li>**3. Development Phase:** Your website is meticulously built from scratch, ensuring clean code, optimal performance, and responsive design.</li>
			<li>**4. Onboarding and Hosting:** I'll assist you with launching your new site, setting up reliable hosting, and providing training to manage your content.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="testimonials site-container">
		<div class="testimonials--inner">
			<h2>What My Clients Say</h2>
			<div class="testimonial--list col-3">
				<div class="testimonial--item">
					<p>"Working with [Your Name/Company Name] was a game-changer for our business. Our new website is not only beautiful but has significantly increased our online leads."</p>
					<p class="client--name">- Jane Doe, CEO of [Client Company 1]</p>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial--item">
					<p>"I'm incredibly impressed with the speed and professionalism. They truly understood our vision and delivered a website that exceeded our expectations."</p>
					<p class="client--name">- John Smith, Founder of [Client Company 2]</p>
				</div>
				<div class="testimonial--item">
					<p>"Our old website was a mess. [Your Name/Company Name] transformed it into a modern, user-friendly platform that our customers love. Highly recommend!"</p>
					<p class="client--name">- Sarah Lee, Marketing Manager at [Client Company 3]</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="faq site-container">
		<div class="faq--inner">
			<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
			<div class="faq--list">
				<div class="faq--item">
					<h3>How long does it take to build a website?</h3>
					<p>The timeline varies depending on the complexity and scope of the project. Typically, a custom website can take anywhere from 4 to 12 weeks from start to finish. We'll provide a more precise timeline after our discovery call.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="faq--item">
					<h3>What is your pricing model?</h3>
					<p>My pricing is tailored to each project, based on your specific requirements and features. I provide a detailed proposal after understanding your needs during the discovery phase. I focus on delivering value that translates into ROI for your business.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="faq--item">
					<h3>Do you offer ongoing maintenance and support?</h3>
					<p>Yes, I offer various post-launch support and maintenance packages to ensure your website remains secure, updated, and performs optimally. We can discuss these options during our consultation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>